BEGIN_PGML

What percent of students ride Bus [$busName]? 

Fill in the blank with a percent. Round your percent to whole numbers, like [`11%`].

*Solution:* Approximately [_________]{$perP} of students ride Bus [$busName]. 

END_PGML

